  "str_2147": "Igiteranyo (Sample 15–49)",
  "str_2149": "🚨 Icyuho Gikomeye: <strong>46.0%</strong> by'abagore bafite imibonano badashyinzwe ntibakoresha uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda. Igikoresho cy'gukurikirana n'isomero ya Rinda biibanda ku itsinda nyakuri.",
  "str_2150": "Ibihamya Birebana n'Amashusho",
  "str_2151": "Rwanda vs. Intego: Icyuho Kimwe",
  "str_2152": "Imibare ivuye mu Rwanda DHS 2025 — ibirindagiro bine bya Rinda biibanda by'ibanze ku ngero enne zimaze gushuka.",
